WEBVTT

00:00:00.199 --> 00:00:02.950
Hey, good morning, family. I was in prayer

00:00:02.960 --> 00:00:05.749
like I normally do, and He said, "I want

00:00:05.759 --> 00:00:08.030
you to teach them how to get strong; I

00:00:08.040 --> 00:00:09.669
want you to teach them how to find their

00:00:09.679 --> 00:00:13.470
own food."There are hard days coming, and

00:00:13.480 --> 00:00:16.029
I need you all to understand that we're

00:00:16.039 --> 00:00:19.189
in a time like never before. This is a

00:00:19.199 --> 00:00:21.990
time that is very serious. We are in the

00:00:22.000 --> 00:00:25.189
last of the last seconds before Jesus

00:00:25.199 --> 00:00:27.230
Christ comes back. Yes, there are things

00:00:27.240 --> 00:00:29.669
that still need to take place. There is a

00:00:29.679 --> 00:00:31.910
great revival that will take

00:00:31.910 --> 00:00:31.920
place—a

00:00:31.920 --> 00:00:35.310
great harvest of souls—but we've got to

00:00:35.320 --> 00:00:37.590
start standing. You need to learn how

00:00:37.600 --> 00:00:40.630
to stand on the Word, your

00:00:40.640 --> 00:00:43.029
Covenant, and the blood. Go over

00:00:43.039 --> 00:00:46.470
Ephesians over and over in the

00:00:46.480 --> 00:00:49.910
book of Acts and Romans, reading

00:00:49.910 --> 00:00:49.920
them

00:00:49.920 --> 00:00:51.990
over and over again so you understand

00:00:52.000 --> 00:00:54.630
who you are in Christ. I'm just trying to

00:00:54.640 --> 00:00:56.150
tell you—a lot of people say

00:00:56.160 --> 00:00:57.349
you're trying to scare us,

00:00:57.349 --> 00:00:57.359
but

00:00:57.359 --> 00:00:59.509
no, I'm trying to prepare you.

00:00:59.519 --> 00:01:01.709
I'm trying to mentally prepare you

00:01:01.719 --> 00:01:03.389
because the more you hear it, the more

00:01:03.399 --> 00:01:06.270
you're going to become ready for it.

00:01:06.280 --> 00:01:08.030
More of these churches are

00:01:08.040 --> 00:01:09.310
preaching compromise; they're not

00:01:09.320 --> 00:01:11.070
teaching you what's going to come and

00:01:11.080 --> 00:01:13.510
what's about to happen. A lot of them are

00:01:13.520 --> 00:01:15.550
just teaching you a little bitty thing

00:01:15.560 --> 00:01:17.149
just to get you to give your offerings

00:01:17.159 --> 00:01:19.109
and your tithes and whatever

00:01:19.119 --> 00:01:21.030
they can get out of you for those

00:01:21.030 --> 00:01:21.040
thirty

00:01:21.040 --> 00:01:23.069
minutes. They teach you a little

00:01:23.069 --> 00:01:23.079
watered-down,

00:01:23.079 --> 00:01:25.390
milky word, and then they send you

00:01:25.400 --> 00:01:27.350
on your way because they don't want to

00:01:27.360 --> 00:01:28.710
ruffle feathers.

00:01:28.720 --> 00:01:30.630
They don't want to cause the big main

00:01:30.640 --> 00:01:33.310
givers to stop coming to church because

00:01:33.320 --> 00:01:34.950
they're the bread of the

00:01:34.960 --> 00:01:36.590
church. They come in there and

00:01:36.600 --> 00:01:39.310
you all bless and sow

00:01:39.310 --> 00:01:39.320
and

00:01:39.320 --> 00:01:41.350
give to these people, but they're not

00:01:41.360 --> 00:01:43.590
teaching you how to stand by faith and

00:01:43.600 --> 00:01:46.310
how to live by faith and how to combat

00:01:46.320 --> 00:01:48.550
what's about to happen. There are some

00:01:48.560 --> 00:01:50.749
really good churches out there, and as

00:01:50.759 --> 00:01:52.590
long as they're preaching and teaching

00:01:52.600 --> 00:01:55.030
you how to stand and live by faith and

00:01:55.040 --> 00:01:57.950
how to combat

00:01:57.960 --> 00:02:00.149
what's coming in the days ahead, then

00:02:00.159 --> 00:02:02.429
you're good. But if you're getting

00:02:02.439 --> 00:02:05.069
a watered-down word and you're not

00:02:05.079 --> 00:02:07.270
hearing the

00:02:07.280 --> 00:02:12.190
truth, run! Run! You've got to know

00:02:12.200 --> 00:02:14.910
this stuff. This is

00:02:14.920 --> 00:02:16.470
part of what the Lord has told me for

00:02:16.480 --> 00:02:20.830
today: a good percentage of you do not know

00:02:20.840 --> 00:02:23.270
how to speak in tongues

00:02:23.270 --> 00:02:23.280
or

00:02:23.280 --> 00:02:24.869
understand the baptism of the Holy

00:02:24.879 --> 00:02:28.229
Spirit at all, and it is very important.

00:02:28.239 --> 00:02:30.110
You all ask me all the time, "How do you

00:02:30.120 --> 00:02:32.270
see the things you see? How do you go

00:02:32.280 --> 00:02:35.150
where you go in the spirit?"It is not by

00:02:35.160 --> 00:02:37.869
praying in English. I get there by

00:02:37.879 --> 00:02:40.390
praying in tongues—praying in the Holy

00:02:40.390 --> 00:02:40.400
Ghost—and

00:02:40.400 --> 00:02:43.670
I do this all the time. I

00:02:43.680 --> 00:02:46.589
practice praying in the spirit. I would

00:02:46.589 --> 00:02:46.599
say—and

00:02:46.599 --> 00:02:48.790
I'm not going to

00:02:48.800 --> 00:02:50.390
exaggerate—probably

00:02:50.400 --> 00:02:53.589
80% of my day, in some way, I'm

00:02:53.599 --> 00:02:55.430
praying in the spirit under my

00:02:55.440 --> 00:02:57.710
breath: driving down the road, doing

00:02:57.720 --> 00:02:59.830
yard work, whatever. I've just practiced.

00:02:59.840 --> 00:03:01.949
It's like lifting weights. I've just

00:03:01.959 --> 00:03:04.309
learned how to practice speaking in

00:03:04.319 --> 00:03:07.309
tongues and doing it all the time.

00:03:07.319 --> 00:03:08.949
Whether I get

00:03:08.959 --> 00:03:10.869
distracted with something

00:03:10.869 --> 00:03:10.879
or

00:03:10.879 --> 00:03:12.550
I'm walking down the hall,

00:03:12.560 --> 00:03:14.229
I'll end up just starting

00:03:14.229 --> 00:03:14.239
to pray

00:03:14.239 --> 00:03:15.789
in tongues or singing

00:03:15.789 --> 00:03:15.799
in

00:03:15.799 --> 00:03:17.149
the

00:03:17.149 --> 00:03:17.159
spirit.

00:03:17.159 --> 00:03:19.750
A lot of people on here go,

00:03:19.760 --> 00:03:22.110
"Well, you can't pray in tongues

00:03:22.120 --> 00:03:23.990
unless you have an

00:03:23.990 --> 00:03:24.000
interpreter."You're

00:03:24.000 --> 00:03:26.149
wrong, and I'm going to prove it today.

00:03:26.159 --> 00:03:27.589
I'm going to show you the scriptures to

00:03:27.599 --> 00:03:30.270
tell you how wrong you are. I pray in

00:03:30.280 --> 00:03:33.149
tongues all the time, and you need to

00:03:33.159 --> 00:03:34.990
know

00:03:36.959 --> 00:03:40.789
this. Just like we have angelic

00:03:40.789 --> 00:03:40.799
presences

00:03:40.799 --> 00:03:43.910
that watch over us, there is a demonic

00:03:43.920 --> 00:03:47.630
presence that is assigned like a

00:03:47.640 --> 00:03:50.149
familiar spirit to

00:03:50.159 --> 00:03:53.149
watch you. When you have that

00:03:53.159 --> 00:03:55.550
demonic spirit that tries to follow you

00:03:55.560 --> 00:03:57.350
around, it tries to watch and hear what

00:03:57.360 --> 00:03:59.229
you're going to be saying because

00:03:59.229 --> 00:03:59.239
your

00:03:59.239 --> 00:04:01.069
life and death is in the

00:04:01.079 --> 00:04:03.470
power of the tongue. What you say out of

00:04:03.480 --> 00:04:05.750
your mouth yesterday is what you're

00:04:05.760 --> 00:04:09.069
living today. It's a process. You

00:04:09.079 --> 00:04:11.789
say and you sow with your mouth and

00:04:11.799 --> 00:04:14.589
you're reaping the harvest the next

00:04:14.599 --> 00:04:17.550
day. You have got to learn that your

00:04:17.560 --> 00:04:20.550
tongue is powerful.

00:04:20.560 --> 00:04:24.590
The enemy listens to your prayers

00:04:24.590 --> 00:04:24.600
and

00:04:24.600 --> 00:04:27.670
tries to see where you're weak

00:04:27.680 --> 00:04:30.189
that day. He watches and he listens

00:04:30.199 --> 00:04:32.670
because he can go back and report, "Well,

00:04:32.680 --> 00:04:34.270
she's having a problem with depression

00:04:34.280 --> 00:04:35.710
because she's praying about depression

00:04:35.710 --> 00:04:35.720
today,"or

00:04:35.720 --> 00:04:37.710
"She's having a problem with

00:04:37.710 --> 00:04:37.720
anxiety,"or

00:04:37.720 --> 00:04:39.390
"She's having a problem with

00:04:39.400 --> 00:04:41.070
her husband and they're fighting, and I

00:04:41.080 --> 00:04:43.710
hear what she's saying in her tongue and

00:04:43.720 --> 00:04:45.790
how she's complaining all the time, so we

00:04:45.800 --> 00:04:47.870
just got to keep putting

00:04:47.870 --> 00:04:47.880
pressure."They

00:04:47.880 --> 00:04:49.510
go back and they

00:04:49.520 --> 00:04:52.110
strategize: "How do I put pressure in that

00:04:52.120 --> 00:04:54.990
area to keep hitting her because we know

00:04:55.000 --> 00:04:56.870
what we're doing is

00:04:59.310 --> 00:04:59.320
working?"You

00:05:01.560 --> 00:05:03.670
start

00:05:03.680 --> 00:05:05.350
saying all this stuff out of your mouth

00:05:05.360 --> 00:05:07.629
and you're praying, "Oh God, I'm

00:05:07.639 --> 00:05:10.550
having a hard time today, God please help

00:05:10.560 --> 00:05:13.310
me. Oh, Johnny's out doing drugs

00:05:13.310 --> 00:05:13.320
again."You're

00:05:13.320 --> 00:05:16.270
interceding. Just like

00:05:16.280 --> 00:05:18.590
how it was in

00:05:18.600 --> 00:05:22.070
army times—you know, you would send a

00:05:22.080 --> 00:05:24.710
pigeon with

00:05:24.710 --> 00:05:24.720
a

00:05:24.720 --> 00:05:26.550
message,

00:05:29.720 --> 00:05:32.309
a secret code

00:05:32.319 --> 00:05:34.390
of what was going on in the battle.

00:05:34.400 --> 00:05:36.629
Then they brought cryptographers in,

00:05:36.639 --> 00:05:38.230
and

00:05:38.240 --> 00:05:40.350
it was a secret message that only

00:05:40.360 --> 00:05:43.029
the really genius people could

00:05:43.039 --> 00:05:45.830
decipher

00:05:45.840 --> 00:05:48.469
because they didn't want the enemy to

00:05:48.479 --> 00:05:50.469
get the battle plans.

00:05:56.639 --> 00:05:58.790
When

00:05:58.800 --> 00:06:00.830
you get in the spirit and you're praying

00:06:00.840 --> 00:06:03.909
in tongues, the enemy does not know what

00:06:03.919 --> 00:06:06.749
you're praying, so he's confused.

00:06:06.759 --> 00:06:08.270
He doesn't want you praying in the

00:06:08.280 --> 00:06:10.469
spirit; that's why it's been hit so hard

00:06:10.479 --> 00:06:12.710
in the body of Christ. Satan has come

00:06:12.720 --> 00:06:15.350
against praying in tongues more than any

00:06:15.360 --> 00:06:17.029
other gift.

00:06:17.039 --> 00:06:19.150
We hear about prophecy

00:06:19.150 --> 00:06:19.160
and

00:06:19.160 --> 00:06:20.230
all these other things,

00:06:20.240 --> 00:06:22.189
and the church has embraced it.

00:06:22.199 --> 00:06:23.830
But if you start talking about praying

00:06:23.840 --> 00:06:27.150
in tongues, the church says it's of the devil.

00:06:27.160 --> 00:06:30.150
I haven't heard anybody in a bar smoking

00:06:30.160 --> 00:06:32.710
weed or drinking or going

00:06:32.710 --> 00:06:32.720
to

00:06:32.720 --> 00:06:36.629
strip clubs praying in

00:06:36.639 --> 00:06:39.150
tongues.

00:06:39.160 --> 00:06:41.749
They're not doing that because if it was

00:06:41.759 --> 00:06:43.950
of the devil, the devil's crowd would be

00:06:43.960 --> 00:06:47.150
doing it. They would be out drinking

00:06:47.160 --> 00:06:49.909
whiskey and praying in tongues. The

00:06:49.919 --> 00:06:52.230
devil wants you to be good at sin.

00:06:56.720 --> 00:06:59.070
Have you ever

00:06:59.080 --> 00:07:02.110
been in an R-rated movie and

00:07:02.110 --> 00:07:02.120
had

00:07:02.120 --> 00:07:04.390
somebody cussing and acting stupid

00:07:04.390 --> 00:07:04.400
while

00:07:04.400 --> 00:07:07.589
praying in tongues? Sin is sin, folks, and

00:07:07.599 --> 00:07:09.749
the devil's a master at keeping people in

00:07:09.759 --> 00:07:12.629
sin. Everyone

00:07:12.629 --> 00:07:12.639
says

00:07:12.639 --> 00:07:14.430
praying in tongues is of the devil, but then why

00:07:14.440 --> 00:07:17.150
is the devil's crowd not doing it?

00:07:17.160 --> 00:07:19.830
Let the elevator go to the top,

00:07:19.840 --> 00:07:22.510
folks.

00:07:22.520 --> 00:07:25.230
It's a gift, and the devil

00:07:25.230 --> 00:07:25.240
has

00:07:25.240 --> 00:07:27.629
deceived the church, trying to

00:07:27.639 --> 00:07:29.950
tell them that it's of the devil

00:07:29.960 --> 00:07:31.510
so you won't want to do it.

00:07:31.520 --> 00:07:33.710
He knows how

00:07:33.720 --> 00:07:35.909
effective the prayer is and how you can

00:07:35.919 --> 00:07:38.950
get in the spirit and whip his butt.

00:07:38.960 --> 00:07:40.589
People

00:07:40.599 --> 00:07:41.990
push it

00:07:42.000 --> 00:07:43.309
back and go, "Well, we don't want this

00:07:43.319 --> 00:07:45.749
in our church because

00:07:45.759 --> 00:07:47.550
it's of the

00:07:47.550 --> 00:07:47.560
devil."All

00:07:47.560 --> 00:07:50.350
you're

00:07:50.360 --> 00:07:52.110
doing is falling

00:07:52.110 --> 00:07:52.120
for

00:07:52.120 --> 00:07:55.070
his evil deceit. Speaking in tongues is a

00:07:55.080 --> 00:07:58.189
tool. When you have the ability

00:07:58.199 --> 00:08:00.550
to give hidden messages to

00:08:00.560 --> 00:08:02.589
the Lord by speaking in tongues—when the

00:08:02.599 --> 00:08:05.029
spirit prays through you and causes

00:08:05.039 --> 00:08:07.309
intercession—you're

00:08:07.319 --> 00:08:09.029
able to pray the mysteries and you're

00:08:09.039 --> 00:08:10.869
hitting the target right on.

00:08:10.879 --> 00:08:12.909
You're not praying out of the flesh; your

00:08:12.919 --> 00:08:15.550
spirit bypasses your brain.

00:08:15.560 --> 00:08:17.629
You're not praying all the

00:08:17.639 --> 00:08:20.550
drama of the day:

00:08:20.560 --> 00:08:22.589
"Well, my boss did me wrong,"or "I'm fighting

00:08:22.599 --> 00:08:25.149
with my

00:08:27.230 --> 00:08:27.240
wife."The

00:08:28.599 --> 00:08:30.110
devil

00:08:32.269 --> 00:08:32.279
is

00:08:34.039 --> 00:08:35.469
over there writing it all

00:08:35.479 --> 00:08:37.829
down.

00:08:37.839 --> 00:08:41.589
Instead,

00:08:41.599 --> 00:08:43.709
you get in

00:08:43.719 --> 00:08:45.470
the spirit and start activating

00:08:45.480 --> 00:08:47.470
your spirit, and it bypasses your brain.

00:08:47.480 --> 00:08:49.430
The

00:08:49.440 --> 00:08:51.470
more you practice, the more you start

00:08:51.480 --> 00:08:53.949
flowing in the Holy Ghost. He's able to

00:08:53.959 --> 00:08:57.470
pray through you and you

00:08:57.480 --> 00:09:00.030
start singing songs in the spirit, just

00:09:00.040 --> 00:09:02.350
like the Apostle

00:09:02.360 --> 00:09:06.110
Paul and Silas

00:09:06.110 --> 00:09:06.120
in

00:09:06.120 --> 00:09:08.630
the prison. The Bible says in

00:09:08.640 --> 00:09:11.150
Acts that they started singing songs in

00:09:11.160 --> 00:09:14.190
the spirit, and the power

00:09:14.200 --> 00:09:16.470
of God filled the jail cell and they

00:09:16.480 --> 00:09:19.190
were set free. There was a great, mighty

00:09:19.200 --> 00:09:21.590
earthquake. You need to know

00:09:21.600 --> 00:09:24.470
the same power that was in

00:09:24.480 --> 00:09:27.750
that jail cell is inside of you.

00:09:33.360 --> 00:09:35.990
I'm telling you, God has a

00:09:36.000 --> 00:09:38.430
plan for your life and a plan to

00:09:38.440 --> 00:09:40.550
set you free. The only way you're

00:09:40.560 --> 00:09:43.030
going to get there in these last days is

00:09:43.040 --> 00:09:45.350
by praying in the spirit. I pray in

00:09:45.360 --> 00:09:46.910
the spirit and intercede in the

00:09:46.920 --> 00:09:48.509
spirit; this stuff happens all the

00:09:48.519 --> 00:09:50.269
time. I'll be praying in the spirit

00:09:50.279 --> 00:09:52.430
about circumstances concerning my wife

00:09:52.440 --> 00:09:55.110
or my kids.

00:09:55.110 --> 00:09:55.120
barely

00:09:55.120 --> 00:09:57.670
seldom do I ever pray in English.

00:09:57.680 --> 00:10:00.509
I do if I'm in

00:10:00.519 --> 00:10:03.430
front of other people because I

00:10:03.440 --> 00:10:06.630
want them to join in with me, but 99% of

00:10:06.630 --> 00:10:06.640
the time... 90%

00:10:06.640 --> 00:10:10.069
of my day is praying in tongues.

00:10:10.079 --> 00:10:11.790
I'm going to give you a scripture;

00:10:11.800 --> 00:10:15.670
this is 1 Corinthians 14:2: 'For he that

00:10:15.680 --> 00:10:18.630
speaketh in an unknown tongue speaketh

00:10:18.640 --> 00:10:22.870
not unto men, but unto God; for no man

00:10:22.880 --> 00:10:25.630
understands him; howbeit in the spirit

00:10:25.640 --> 00:10:28.389
he speaketh mysteries.'Here is another

00:10:28.399 --> 00:10:32.550
scripture I want to give you, Jude

00:10:32.550 --> 00:10:32.560
1:20:

00:10:32.560 --> 00:10:35.590
'But ye, beloved, building up yourself on

00:10:35.600 --> 00:10:38.910
your most holy faith, praying in the Holy

00:10:38.910 --> 00:10:38.920
Ghost.'So

00:10:38.920 --> 00:10:41.790
the Holy Spirit is making

00:10:41.800 --> 00:10:45.269
intercession for you whenever you are

00:10:45.279 --> 00:10:47.710
praying and yielding yourself over to

00:10:47.720 --> 00:10:50.550
the Holy Spirit. He is praying through

00:10:50.560 --> 00:10:53.389
you and making intercession through you.

00:10:53.399 --> 00:10:55.790
For

00:10:55.800 --> 00:10:59.430
we know not what we should pray for

00:10:59.440 --> 00:11:02.670
as we ought, but the Spirit itself maketh

00:11:02.680 --> 00:11:05.350
intercession for us with groanings which

00:11:05.360 --> 00:11:08.710
cannot be uttered. It comes out

00:11:08.710 --> 00:11:08.720
because,

00:11:08.720 --> 00:11:10.190
like I said, when you're praying in

00:11:10.200 --> 00:11:11.829
your intellect and

00:11:11.839 --> 00:11:15.030
your natural mind, and you're praying

00:11:15.040 --> 00:11:17.470
all the things of your flesh,

00:11:17.480 --> 00:11:19.470
and you're asking God, 'Well, I

00:11:19.480 --> 00:11:21.190
need this and that,'you don't even know

00:11:21.200 --> 00:11:23.030
what you really need. You don't even know

00:11:23.040 --> 00:11:26.150
how to get the outcome in the natural

00:11:26.160 --> 00:11:27.949
for what you're going through.

00:11:27.959 --> 00:11:29.509
Your marriage could be in

00:11:29.519 --> 00:11:31.509
trouble, or your kids could be in trouble,

00:11:31.519 --> 00:11:32.990
but you're praying only what your

00:11:33.000 --> 00:11:35.269
intellect knows. Instead of shooting

00:11:35.279 --> 00:11:38.030
blindly at a target,

00:11:38.040 --> 00:11:40.110
you're hitting the target on

00:11:40.120 --> 00:11:41.790
the bullseye when you're praying in

